                        rewrite selected text user has prose wants clearer shorter more professional version                                                                            Rewrite selected text                                           Use rewrite when the user has selected prose and wants a clearer, shorter, more professional version.                                                                                           professional tone keep message direct polite concrete free jokes filler unsupported claims                                                                      Professional tone                                               Keep the message direct, polite, concrete, and free of jokes, filler, or unsupported claims.                                                                                                    formal memo subject line one-sentence purpose short body paragraphs explicit next action                                                                        Formal memo                                                     Use a subject line, one-sentence purpose, short body paragraphs, and an explicit next action.                                                                                                   summar summary action summaries preserve dates names decisions requested actions while dropping repeated explanation                                            Summary action                                                  Summaries should preserve dates, names, decisions, and requested actions while dropping repeated explanation.                                                                                   shorten action shortening keep original intent remove qualifiers duplicate phrases low-value background                                                         Shorten action                                                  Shortening should keep the original intent and remove qualifiers, duplicate phrases, and low-value background.                                                                                  clarify clarity action state happened matters next keep artifact tag checksum test details concrete                                                             Clarity action                                                  State what happened, why it matters, and the next action; keep artifact, tag, checksum, and test details concrete.                                                                              status update direct polite wording include current blocker end next action timing                                                                              Status update                                                   Use direct polite wording, include the current blocker, and end with the next action or timing.                                                                                                 status update shape state current result blocker next action expected timing                                                                                    Status update shape                                             State the current result, the blocker, the next action, and the expected timing.                                                                                                                release note shape lead changed list proof state any known limits plainly                                                                                       Release note shape                                              Lead with what changed, list proof, then state any known limits plainly.                                                                                                                        bug report shape include expected behavior actual reproduction steps logs suspected area                                                                        Bug report shape                                                Include expected behavior, actual behavior, reproduction steps, logs, and the suspected area.                                                                                                   executive summary give decision evidence risk requested action short paragraphs                                                                                 Executive summary                                               Give the decision, the evidence, the risk, and the requested action in short paragraphs.                                                                                                        email reply answer direct question first add context next steps                                                                                                 Email reply                                                     Answer the direct question first, then add context and next steps.                                                                                                                              rewrite rules preserve facts remove filler keep tone polite avoid unsupported claims                                                                            Rewrite rules                                                   Preserve facts, remove filler, keep the tone polite, and avoid unsupported claims.                                                                                                              checklist writing short action verbs make item independently testable                                                                                           Checklist writing                                               Use short action verbs and make each item independently testable.                                                                                                                               handoff note say done remains evidence lives who owns next action                                                                                               Handoff note                                                    Say what is done, what remains, where evidence lives, and who owns the next action.                                                                                                             meeting notes capture decisions owners dates open questions follow-up actions                                                                                   Meeting notes                                                   Capture decisions, owners, dates, open questions, and follow-up actions.                                                                                                                        project plan list goal milestones owners risks next checkpoint                                                                                                  Project plan                                                    List the goal, milestones, owners, risks, and the next checkpoint.                                                                                                                              track risks risk register record impact likelihood mitigation owner review date                                                                                 Risk register                                                   For each risk, record impact, likelihood, mitigation, owner, and review date.                                                                                                                   csv cleanup keep headers stable quote fields commas normalize dates preserve untouched source copy                                                              CSV cleanup                                                     Keep headers stable, quote fields with commas, normalize dates, and preserve an untouched source copy.                                                                                          spreadsheet formula state input cells expected result one check errors                                                                                          Spreadsheet formula                                             State the input cells, the formula, the expected result, and one check for errors.                                                                                                              budget table show item cost owner due date status totals checked quickly                                                                                        Budget table                                                    Show item, cost, owner, due date, and status so totals can be checked quickly.                                                                                                                  polite email start answer add one reason state next step keep tone direct                                                                                       Polite email                                                    Start with the answer, add one reason, state the next step, and keep the tone direct.                                                                                                           decision memo state recommendation alternatives considered evidence risks owner                                                                                 Decision memo                                                   State the recommendation, alternatives considered, evidence, risks, and owner.                                                                                                                  user docs write task goal prerequisites exact steps expected result troubleshooting note                                                                        User docs                                                       Write the task goal, prerequisites, exact steps, expected result, and troubleshooting note.                                                                                             